  <!-- ============ SECTION 09 — INDUSTRY CONTEXT (NEW in v8 — supernode topics) ============ -->
  <!-- Per §7.4 of the rules: 6–8 topics, ~150 words each, 2–3 Tier 1 cites
       per paragraph. Establishes the page as the topical supernode in Google's
